md:
giải nghĩa từ "carrying" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

* Carrying (verb) - mang, cầm, mang theo
	+ Meaning: to hold or support something while moving
	+ Example: She was carrying a heavy bag on her shoulder.
	+ Related words: carry, carrier, carriage

* Carrying (verb) - thực hiện, tiến hành
	+ Meaning: to perform or execute an action
	+ Example: The company is carrying out a new marketing strategy.
	+ Related words: carry, carry out, carry on

* Carrying (verb) - mang thai
	+ Meaning: to be pregnant with a child
	+ Example: She is carrying her second child.
	+ Related words: carry, pregnancy, childbirth

* Carrying (adjective) - mang, cầm
	+ Meaning: having or holding something
	+ Example: The carrying capacity of the elevator is 10 people.
	+ Related words: carry, carrier, carriage
